{"tid":1549642,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"津貼中學學生權利你要知","createTime":"2019-09-07T11:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:22:43.000Z","uid":134683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef43ea8e84c78b050a20066c743cfed426bdea0","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"首先係大家最關心既踢學生出校程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有津貼學校都受資助則例管<br />\n雖然管學生入學同踢出校最大權果個係教育局常任秘書長<br />\n但香港有普及教育以黎<br />\n只有迫學校收生而冇迫學校踢學生走<br />\n因為香港教育條例同原則都係以學生利益行先<br />\n即係學生返學接受教育權利係有絕對既保障<br />\n所以就算資助則例寫明edb有權踢<br />\n基於上述原則佢地係唔可能踢學生出校<br />\n<br />\n根據資助則例<br />\n踢學生出校有兩個條件<br />\n1）冇交錢，資助則例冇寫明咩錢，一般理解係以前高中既堂費，但今時今日就冇修改呢項條文<br />\n2）校內犯大錯，同家長合作過而繼續犯事<br />\n校監同意的話就可以踢學生走，事後知會教育局常任秘書長"},{"pid":"69af29103581f83aa9bd1c2e580f17da5ec4c421","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"真係俾人踢出校可以㸃？<br />\n<br />\n學校就算踢左你出校<br />\n你係有絕對權利返原校讀書<br />\n除左因為受入學令既保障外<br />\nLast attended school係有最大責任收失學學生"},{"pid":"7298725190e1378f553cce5a4ec04d649d8f6d2d","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"踢學生走最大權其實係校監<br />\n不過因為佢唔可能識個學生<br />\n一定係校長、副校或訓導主任話事<br />\n如果你學校咁唔好彩上述嗰幾個都係藍絲就麻煩d<br />\n但任何學校都怕傳媒同怕家長<br />\n就算左派學校都唔可能因政見而踢學生走<br />\n如果屋企家境好既<br />\n見家長時叫埋律師去學校<br />\n唔好話踢<br />\n記個缺點都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇家底既就搵葉建源同蘋果<br />\n由葉建源同教育局deal"},{"pid":"08eabf96dde2cb98e90e0eac963c88f879405e52","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b543f6033c76560c156c3a1f52561d3b34e3fa65","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c280ef59d6b4860efa57f6b51369aecc468802","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1539f90f764210d51748a2459b34aef5a16102b","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e104a634dd82eca92033d94d5c4de8b60c82d41","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5beee0d5cb02dfba497117aef14bf375f7fbb1","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a027fc48b9c9e522bbcacf22d1d943e4ee1f9c8e","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c86526061f961023dce9c17c449d162f45305f","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42b2d6a5c15eff450416be95a2d3831b10b2539","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb0c8092b6f571c9630a3a863d0163e7b714351","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd7daede293a702213b3bca60a2d2b1947613f7","tid":1549642,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"